parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description:
The ID of the cluster.

You can call the [ListClusters](~~87116~~) operation to query the cluster ID.

parameters.name: ContainerType
parameters.description: The type of the container. Set the value to singularity.

parameters.name: ImageTag
parameters.description:
The tags of the image.

Default value: latest

parameters.name: Repository
parameters.description:
The name of the repository.

You can call the [ListContainerImages](~~87348~~) operation to query the name of the repository.
